aju t-xaq. Aju t-xob'il ex aju tq'oj tzaj tuj tanmi ik tza'n t-xu'k; xi t-xo´n t-xaq u´j extzen xi t-xo´n, tuk´e tkyaqil tipumal, twitz muro, jatumel n-ok tmojb´an tib´ tuk´a txqantl
tz´is n-chi b´aj t-xmo´n ti´j t-xu´k n-chi b´aj t-xo´n.
Xi tzyet tu´n t-xi´ b´et toj tkyaqil ja, n-chi jaqet qe cajón mya b´a´n extzen
n-chi tzaj t-chmo´n u´j noq tun t-xi t-chjet kyi´j junx t-xaq, noq ch´in t-xilen
ti n-b´ant tu´n, tze´nku junjun frases aleatorias te t-xnaq´tzb´il Rita n-chi b´itzin toj twi´:
